 	 *     local_tlb_gen == 1, mm_tlb_gen == 3, and end != TLB_FLUSH_ALL.
-	 *    If we were to use __flush_tlb_single() and set local_tlb_gen to
+	 *    If we were to use __flush_tlb_one_user() and set local_tlb_gen to
